A Favorites Mechanism (#5121)

A patch favorites mechanism

1. A UI for them (a heart; a submenu under user patches if you ahve em)
2. A storage in the Favorites part of the DB which doesn't get nuked on schema
3. And all the associated code changes to make the right thing happen at the
   right time.